  "details": "ruoyi-vue-pro through 2026.05, fixed in commit c779a47, contains a missing authorization vulnerability in the CRM module's GET /admin-api/crm/follow-up-record/get endpoint that allows authenticated users to read any follow-up record by iterating sequential numeric IDs. Attackers can exploit this by sending requests with arbitrary ID parameters to access other users' follow-up notes, file attachments, scheduling information, and business entity references without proper authorization checks.",
